Master Answer:
We do not provide travel vaccines or specific recommendations at ImmunizeBC.  Please contact your health care provider or a travel clinic to find out which vaccines are recommended for your travel destination. You can find a list of travel clinics in BC here.
When travelling outside of Canada, you may be at risk for a number of diseases that are rarely found in Canada but are common in other parts of the world.
You can find more information on travel vaccinations here.
